Package: ngreg
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Sparse Regression with Normal Gamma Priors
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-02-16
Author: Carson McKee
Maintainer: Carson McKee <carson.mckee@kcl.ac.uk>
Description: This package implements Bayesian regression using the Normal-Gamma shrinkage prior described by Griffin & Brown (2010). This particularly suited to problems where the number of observations is small relative to the number of predictors. 
License: GPLv3
Imports: Rcpp, RcppEigen
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
NeedsCompilation: yes
